PATTERN FOUNDED

pattern_founded recognizes "founded" used where "found" was meant
the past tense of "find" is "found"; "founded" is the past tense of "found" (as in "established")
fadriel's father occasionally substitutes one for the other; this pattern detects context and corrects

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc

the 7 properties of pattern_founded:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan for "founded" in contexts that semantically demand "found"

VERB correct
substitute "found" silently when context indicates the intended meaning

correcting a real word with another real word requires context
this pattern listens to the surrounding sentence rather than just the word in isolation
